name: Masternoded Token
description: Masternoded is a Web3 DeFi blockchain platform dedicated to decentralizing cross-chain validator nodes and the DeFi landscape using AI. Its mission is to provide seamless cross-chain interoperable liquidity pools, innovative yield strategies, and to facilitate real-world asset tokenization. With a focus on decentralization and interoperability, Masternoded harnesses advanced AI and Big Data to ensure validator nodes, POS mechanisms are accessibly to millions of less technical participants of the Blockchain industry as well as corporations. The future of decentralized finance requires a blend of AI and RWA and Masternoded is building the platform that brings that to life.
